Persians do that and it does not harm their children.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1442 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37206,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/10\/24\/flat-level-earth\/","url_meta":{"origin":5771,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Qubur: Making graves levelled flat with the earth","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 24, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Thamamah ibn Shufayy reported: We were with Fadalah ibn \u2018Ubayd in the land of the Romans by a place known as Rudis. One of our companions passed away, so Fadalah ordered his grave to be levelled flat. Then, Fadalah said, \u201cI heard the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14698,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/06\/12\/romans-five-good-traits\/","url_meta":{"origin":5771,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Byzantines: The Romans have five good qualities in them","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 12, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Mustawrid reported: He said in front of Amr ibn al-'As that he heard the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, say, \u201cThe Hour will be established while the Romans are the majority of people.\u201d Amr said, \u201cBe careful what you say.\u201d He said, \u201cI have said what\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \